```
const retryAfter = response.headers.get('Retry-After');
const retryMs = retryAfter ? Number(retryAfter) * 1000 : undefined;
```

2. Lines 174-175 (in apiRaw function):
```
const retryAfter = response.headers.get('Retry-After');
